    Scope and Contents
The Faculty Senate  Ad Hoc Committees records (1981-) consist of agendas,  minutes,  memos,  procedures,  policies surveys and resolutions from various task forces and committees including the Public Safety Task Force, Child Care Task Force, Sexual Harassment Committee, Presidential and VPAA Search Committees, Graduate Curriculum Task Force and Evaluation of the President at SSU.

Ad Hoc committees rarely last more than one academic year; these records document these short term deliberations and decisions concerning SSU.  
  
